# Json to UEFN

A simple tool for converting FModel JSON map exports into text you can paste into UEFN.

## What this app does

- Converts one or more Json files you can get from FModel
- Reads actor, mesh, transform, and world data from the JSON.
- Lets you copy the generated output or save it as a `.txt` file.
- Includes optional helpers for missing assets, nature fallback assets, and Valkyrie / valid asset manifest checking.

## Notes

Converted maps are not guaranteed to be perfect. Some assets, materials, models, or transforms may need manual cleanup inside UEFN.

Keep the original JSON files backed up in case you need to convert again.

Join the server if you need help with anything!
https://discord.gg/SRJVuBjYV
